// Find district with postcodes
const findDistrictWithPostCodes = () => {
    let finalResult = []

    for (let i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
        const district = data[i]
        const postCodeArr = []
        const postCodeResults = postcodes.filter(postcode => postcode.district_id === district.id)

        if (postCodeResults && postCodeResults.length) {
            for (let j = 0; j < postCodeResults.length; j++) {
                const element = postCodeResults[j]
                postCodeArr.push({
                    postCode: element.postCode,
                    postOffice: element.postOffice,
                    upazila: element.upazila,
                    label: element.postCode + " - " + element.postOffice,
                    value: element.postCode
                })
            }
        }

        finalResult.push({
            label: `${district.name} - ${district.bn_name}`,
            value: district.name,
            postCodes: postCodeArr
        })
    }

    return finalResult
}

export const districts = findDistrictWithPostCodes()
